dc_title_s: Dover Strait, Zeebrugge to Boulogne-sur-Mer and Thames Estuary (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From British Admiralty charts to 2006." "Copyright 2007 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes index to next larger scale charts and source diagram. Georeferenced nautical chart. Map no. 37120. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
